eng_questions = '''How can discarded towels be reused?;How can hotels utilize discarded towels to create items that bring joy to guests?;Please help me find 3 items that can be made from repurposed old towels.;Now set as a waste recycling designer, there is a project for a hotel disposing of towels. Please provide three recycling solutions that customers can use perfectly.;Please help me repurpose towels into different products.;Please provide examples of transforming waste using towels.;Please propose three ideas for reusing discarded old towels in urban hotels, providing items for "business travelers, conference participants, friends and family of patients, and travelers.";I recently participated in a creative product design competition and need some ideas.;Designing products from old towels, your identity is: fashion designer. If you were to design products using old towels, how would you do it?;What innovative things can be done with towel recycling?'''
